=========================================================================
Third-party protocol compatibility
=========================================================================

This project implements a minimal subset of the following open protocols.
No third-party code is vendored — only wire-format compatibility:

- A2A (Agent-to-Agent) Protocol v0.3
  Spec: https://a2a-protocol.org/latest/specification/
  Used by: bin/mmteam-a2a-server.py

- MCP (Model Context Protocol)
  Spec: https://spec.modelcontextprotocol.io
  Used by: bin/mmteam-mcp.py

